reviewText: This is a great movie. The acting was superb and the plot was awesome. These things happen to us in life. Just as we think we've got it all sometimes the bottom does drop out from under us. I enjoyed the way David E. Talbert handled the plot. There were some funny moments,, some sad moments, and some moments that made you go humm.... what would I do in that situation? I would definitely recommend it to a friend. Keep up the good work David E Talbert !!
Title: David E. Talbert's Suddenly Single

reviewText: After being disappointed by black plays with the same tired and hashed-over plots and over the top buffoonery, I was very pleasantly surprised by this production. It had just the right touch of humor and drama, and had me laughing one minute and tearing up the next. The acting was superbly professional. If you want to see a refreshing and satisfying play, check this one out! You will not be disappointed.
